title: Little Shannon Dudley - New/Age/Jeezus [2015]
description:
Little Shannon Dudley has returned with a new album, two years in the making! New Age Jeezus, featuring Daddy K-Rav, Riley Barnes, and Tyler Two of the Macaroni and Cheese Gang, the less-than-anticipated follow-up to The Kristine LP, this album features songs about nothing, pro wrestling references, a Presidential bid, and even a bullshit Vine trend song. A hybrid between a rap album and an instrumental album, you're guaranteed to not hate this nearly as much as the last album!
